{"id":643721,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/05/圣谛-一个鸟窝拆出的顶级幽默/","date":"2020-05-10T22:36:18Z","modified":"2020-05-10T23:30:27Z","title":"圣谛 | 一个鸟窝拆出的顶级幽默","content":"<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-643722\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/1-13.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"803\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/1-13.jpg 752w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/1-13-187x300.jpg 187w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/1-13-638x1024.jpg 638w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>讲真，别说拆了个鸟窝，有需要就算拆人窝，又怎么了？</p>\n<div class=\"text_exposed_show\">\n<p>说需要，也别说什么发展是需要，领导的车要干净、要体面，就不是需要了？大众矫情过分嘛。</p>\n<p>这几天帝都拆鸟窝的事成了热点，我木有别的想法，就是感觉帝都人要是幽默起来，那真连赵本山都赶不上啊。</p>\n<p>拆鸟窝未必是灵道意思，灵道日理万机哪里顾得了那么多？下面人急灵道所急，想灵道所想，也不算大错。虽然作风粗暴了一点，也不失一个好态度。</p>\n<p>就是办的太幽默。</p>\n<p>本来随便找个理由搪塞过去也就是了，比如：疫情期间为避免野生鸟类传播疫情，所以要拆窝。</p>\n<p>说不定还能拿个防疫先进奖。</p>\n<p>但他们就直说了，说有鸟粪掉灵道车上，他们才搞出这个动静</p>\n<p>太不成熟，搞的有点被动，显得灵道作风太不亲鸟。</p>\n<p>一上热搜，他们就有点捉急，有点现出了小里小气的贼形&#8230;.</p>\n<p>我估计是紧张了，不紧张拆个鸟窝，紧张给灵道造成的影响不好&#8230;</p>\n<p>一紧张，动作就走形，横幅拉的有点露怯，说的好像这里还有别的什么人，嫌弃鸟的声音大了似的</p>\n<p>好像这里还有什么人，能随随便便拿个工程车出来踹鸟窝似的</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-643723\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/2-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"418\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/2-2.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/2-2-300x251.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/2-2-1024x855.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/2-2-768x641.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>拉个横幅还不够</p>\n<p>还要出摊子发放亲鸟宣传册，摆出一副要教育群众的架势</p>\n<p>群众路线不是这样走的呀，朋友！</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-643724\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/3-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"503\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/3-1.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/3-1-298x300.jpg 298w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/3-1-1018x1024.jpg 1018w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/3-1-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/3-1-768x772.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/3-1-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>最后，他们干了一件最最最幽默的事，贴出了个告示，让大家举报“到底是他妈谁拆了鸟窝”</p>\n<p>还有线索就通知他们，好像他们家里都不装镜子一样：</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-643725\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/4-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"314\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/4-2.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/4-2-300x188.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/4-2-1024x643.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/4-2-768x482.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/4-2-400x250.jpg 400w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>同时派了一辆车，去装了个假鸟窝：</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-643726\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/5-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"695\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/5-1.jpg 408w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/5-1-216x300.jpg 216w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>好事者眼尖，说咦，这不就是那个拆鸟窝的车吗？</p>\n<p>到底是讲相声的地方，学说逗唱，全了&#8230;.</p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\"text_exposed_show\">\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n","author":1057,"categories":[18271,38912,38985],"tags":[9363,15779,40435]}